==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alloy steel
<hw>Al"loy steel</hw>. <def>Any steel containing a notable quantity of
some other metal alloyed with the iron, usually chromium, nickel,
manganese, tungsten, or vanadium.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

